ely holds critical information. I should read through the script or task prompt and consider if adjustments are needed to ensure it detects installed skills and possibly implement an auto-update feature for relevant ones.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我先把这个“检查 GitHub 更新”的定时任务源头、最近一次输出、以及它到底怎么判断“已安装/未安装”查清楚。然后我直接给你修，不只做解释。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3ac7b405e714490169e432ef3bc4819abfda3c719b3629a0\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3uG4bK6CWdxna8pXaRtvzBCC|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e432ef68c0819ab9554e3ead5b30af","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\nprintf '%s\\n' '--- find github update cron job ---'\ngrep -n \"github_repo_update\\|GitHub\\|repo update\\|更新检查\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json | head -n 80\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- latest github update reports ---'\nls -lt /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update* 2>/dev/null || true\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- latest report content ---'\nsed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_latest.md 2>/dev/null || true\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- recent cron session around 09:00 ---'\nsed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/agents/coding-agent/sessions/d6d9141d-ce1f-469f-b09b-93675ae4349e.jsonl 2>/dev/null || true","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":30,"yieldMs":1000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -e\\nprintf '%s\\\\n' '--- find github update cron job ---'\\ngrep -n \\\"github_repo_update\\\\|GitHub\\\\|repo update\\\\|更新检查\\\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json | head -n 80\\nprintf '\\\\n%s\\\\n' '--- latest github update reports ---'\\nls -lt /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update* 2>/dev/null || true\\nprintf '\\\\n%s\\\\n' '--- latest report content ---'\\nsed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_latest.md 2>/dev/null || true\\nprintf '\\\\n%s\\\\n' '--- recent cron session around 09:00 ---'\\nsed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/agents/coding-agent/sessions/d6d9141d-ce1f-469f-b09b-93675ae4349e.jsonl 2>/dev/null || true\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":30,\"yieldMs\":1000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":175046,"output":845,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":175891,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776562909276,"responseId":"resp_0b3ac7b405e714490169e432dff668819aa4114fdb784beab5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5af9e4df","parentId":"4316d6f3","timestamp":"2026-04-19T01:42:12.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3uG4bK6CWdxna8pXaRtvzBCC|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e432ef68c0819ab9554e3ead5b30af","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"--- find github update cron job ---\n746:      \"name\": \"每日自动更新检查\",\n759:        \"message\": \"执行以下更新检查并推送摘要：\\n\\n1. **Skills 更新检查**：运行 `python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py`，这个脚本会：\\n   - 对\\\"本地有改动\\\"的 skill，实际检查改动内容（是否涉及高风险模式如 eval/subprocess/crypto），给出明确建议：保留/更新/review\\n   - 区分\\\"未安装\\\"vs\\\"轻量定制\\\"vs\\\"有git追踪\\\"\\n   - 报告汇总：⚠️需review、🔄可更新、✅保留本地、⏭未安装\\n\\n2. **OpenClaw 版本检查**（只读）：运行 `openclaw --version` 查看当前版本，再查询 npm 最新版本（`npm show clawhub version`），判断是否需要升级。**不要执行实际升级**。\\n\\n3. **汇总输出**：按格式输出结果表格，最后给出明确结论。\\n\\n推送摘要即可，不需要详细展开每个 skill 的文件列表。\",\n\n--- latest github update reports ---\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  staff  21024 Apr 19 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_state_20260419.json\n-rw-------  1 ling  staff   4366 Apr 19 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_latest.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  staff   4366 Apr 19 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_report_20260419.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  staff  21024 Apr 18 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_state_20260418.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  staff   4366 Apr 18 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_report_20260418.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  staff  20435 Apr 17 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_state_20260417.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  staff   4422 Apr 17 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_report_20260417.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  staff  20092 Apr 16 09:00 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_state_20260416.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 ling  sta