 address the task now. First, I should inspect the `skill_update_check.py` and the state JSON, focusing on potential scheduled task sources in `jobs.json`. I might need to read the current report state to spot any misclassifications and edit the script to allow auto-updates for worthwhile tasks. I have to consider committing changes after those edits in the coding-agent workspace. I'll check the `skill_update_check.py` along with the latest state JSON and see if I need to use the clawhub skill for updates.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Debugging update checker task**\\n\\nI’m currently debugging the update checker task. It’s not absolutely necessary to use it, so I might consider skipping it if it complicates things. Instead, I should focus on inspecting `jobs.json` alongside the relevant job and script. This way, I'll have a clearer understanding of the scheduled tasks and potentially identify any issues that need addressing. It’s all about piecing together the right information for a smoother process!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我把这条任务的“脑子”和“手”都拆开看：  \n- 脑子 = cron prompt  \n- 手 = `skill_update_check.py`  \n\n先看它为什么会把本地已装 skill 说成没装，再把“值得更新就自动更新”这条逻辑补上。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3ac7b405e714490169e43302fc70819ab7d12a6b2e7ebb4f\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_FpsWtA729njNetCJgCjDIuE9|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e433040974819aa2c4c970ccddbb66","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py","limit":400},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py\",\"limit\":400}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1qgNIMUDYlE9dLtXbTuYPrYU|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4330409e0819abb970118574aed04","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_state_20260419.json","limit":320},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/github_repo_update_state_20260419.json\",\"limit\":320}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8pfszGvNlmkqcZ2D4XplSWbO|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4330409e8819abd5682334e30c66c","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json","offset":730,"limit":60},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json\",\"offset\":730,\"limit\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":115374,"output":429,"cacheRead":67584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":183387,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776562932476,"responseId":"resp_0b3ac7b405e714490169e432f71ba8819a9d7111b402489b78"}}
{"type":"message","id":"874c3788","parentId":"51f59748","timestamp":"2026-04-19T01:42:29.056Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_FpsWtA729njNetCJgCjDIuE9|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e433040974819aa2c4c970ccddbb66","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSkill Update Checker v4 — 正确路径版本\nSkills 实际路径: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n\"\"\"\n\nimport subprocess\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nHOME = Path.home()\nSKILL_DIR = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\" / \"skills\"   # 正确路径\nWORKSPACE = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\n\n\ndef run_cmd(cmd: str, timeout: int = 10) -> tuple[str, int]:\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(cmd, shell=True, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=timeout)\n        return result.stdout.strip(), result.returncode\n    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n        return \"\", -1\n    except Exception as e:\n        return str(e), -1\n\n\ndef get_installed_skills() -> list[dict]:\n    \"\"\"从 clawhub list 获取已安装 skills\"\"\"\n    stdout, rc = run_cmd(\"clawhub list\")\n    if rc != 0 or not stdout:\n        return []\n    return [{\"name\": p[0], \"version\": p[1]} for p in [l.strip().split() for l in stdout.strip().split(\"\\n\")] if len(p) >= 2]\n\n\ndef check_skill(skill_name: str) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"检查单个 skill\"\"\"\n    skill_path = SKILL_DIR / skill_name\n    exists = skill_path.exists()\n    \n    if not exists:\n        return {\n            \"name\": skill_name,\n            \"status\": \"not_installed\",\n            \"risk\": \"-\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⏭ 未安装\",\n            \"reason\": \"本地不存在\",\n            \"installed\": False,\n        }\n    \n    # 检查 .git\n    has_git = (skill_path / \".git\").exists()\n    \n    # 统计代码文件\n    code_files = []\n    all_files = []\n    try:\n        for f in skill_path.rglob(\"*\"):\n            if f.is_file() and \".git\" not in str(f) and \"node_modules\" not in str(f):\n                rel = str(f.relative_to(skill_path))\n                all_files.append(rel)\n                if f.suffix in [\".py\", \".js\", \".sh\"]:\n                    code_files.append(rel)\n    except:\n        pass\n    \n    code_count = len(code_files)\n    \n    # 高风险代码检查（只查代码文件）\n    risk_samples = []\n    try:\n        for f in skill_path.rglob(\"*\"):\n            if f.is_file() and f.suffix in [\".py\", \".js\", \".sh\"]:\n                if \".git\" in str(f) or \"node_modules\" in str(f):\n                    continue\n                try:\n                    content = f.read_text(errors=\"ignore\", size=8000)\n                    for pattern in [\"eval(\", \"exec(\", \"subprocess(\", \"os.system(\", \"requests.\", \"shell=True\"]:\n                        if pattern in content:\n                            rel = str(f.relative_to(skill_path))\n                            risk_samples.append(f\"{rel}:{pattern}\")\n                except:\n                    pass\n    except:\n        pass\n    \n    # 判断状态\n    if risk_samples:\n        status = \"needs_review\"\n        risk = \"HIGH\"\n        recommendation = \"⚠️ 需review\"\n        reason = f\"代码含: {risk_samples[0]}\"\n    elif not has_git and code_count > 3:\n        status = \"likely_modified\"\n        risk = \"MEDIUM\"\n        recommendation = \"🔍 建议保留\"\n        reason = f\"无git，有{code_count}个代码文件，可能有定制\"\n    elif has_git:\n        # 检查是否有未提交改动（git status --porcelain）\n        status_out, _ = run_cmd(f\"cd {skill_path} && git status --porcelain 2>/dev/null\", timeout=5)\n        has_changes = bool(status_out.strip())\n        if has_changes:\n            diff_stat, _ = run_cmd(f\"cd {skill_path} && git diff --stat 2>/dev/null\", timeout=5)\n            status = \"has_local_changes\"\n            risk = \"LOW\"\n            recommendation = \"✅ 保留本地\"\n            reason = f\"有本地改动: {diff_stat.strip()[:80]}\" if diff_stat else \"有本地改动\"\n        else:\n            status = \"clean\"\n            risk = \"LOW\"\n            recommendation = \"🔄 可更新\"\n            reason = \"与远程无差异\"\n    else:\n        status = \"light_modification\"\n        risk = \"LOW\"\n        recommendation = \"✅ 保留本地\"\n        reason = f\"轻量定制（{code_count}个代码文件）\"\n    \n    return {\n        \"name\": skill_name,\n        \"status\": status,\n        \"risk\": risk,\n        \"recommendation\": recommendation,\n        \"reason\": reason,\n        \"installed\": True,\n        \"has_git\": has_git,\n        \"code_count\": code_count,\n        \"file_count\": len(all_files),\n    }\n\n\ndef main():\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    print(\"🔍 Skill Update Checker v4 — 正确路径\")\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    print(f\"\\n📂 Skills 目录: {SKILL_DIR}\")\n    \n    skills = get_installed_skills()\n    print(f\"📦 clawhub 记录: {len(skills)} 个\\n\")\n    \n    results = []\n    for s in skills:\n        r = check_skill(s[\"name\"])\n        r[\"version\"] = s[\"version\"]\n        results.append(r)\n    \n    # 分列显示\n    print(\"┌\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┐\")\n    print(f\"│ {'Skill':<26} {'风险':^5} {'建议':^22} │\")\n    print(\"├\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┤\")\n    for r in results:\n        rec = r.get(\"recommendation\", \"⏭ 跳过\")\n        risk = r.get(\"risk\", \"-\")\n        name = r[\"name\"][:25]\n        print(f\"│ {name:<26} {risk:^5} {rec[:20]:^22} │\")\n    print(\"└\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┘\")\n    \n    # 分类汇总\n    high = [r for r in results if r[\"risk\"] == \"HIGH\"]\n    med = [r for r in results if r[\"risk\"] == \"MEDIUM\"]\n    clean = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"clean\"]\n    changes = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"has_local_changes\"]\n    light = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] in (\"light_modification\", \"likely_modified\")]\n    not_inst = [r for r in results if not r[\"installed\"]]\n    \n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 62)\n    print(\"📋 详细分析\")\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    \n    if high:\n        print(f\"\\n⚠️  需review（{len(high)} 个）：\")\n        for r in high:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r['reason']}\")\n    \n    if med:\n        print(f\"\\n🔍 建议保留（{len(med)} 个）：\")\n        for r in med:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r['reason']}\")\n    \n    if clean:\n        print(f\"\\n🔄 可更新（{len(clean)} 个）：\")\n        for r in clean:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n    \n    if changes:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 保留本地（{len(changes)} 个，有git改动）：\")\n        for r in changes:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n            print(f\"    {r['reason']}\")\n    \n    if light:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 保留本地（{len(light)} 个，轻量定制）：\")\n        for r in light:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n    \n    if not_inst:\n        print(f\"\\n⏭  未安装（{len(not_inst)} 个）：\")\n        for r in not_inst:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n📊 汇总：⚠️{len(high)} 🔍{len(med)} 🔄{len(clean)} ✅{len(changes)+len(light)} ⏭{len(not_inst)}\")\n    \n    # 保存\n    out = WORKSPACE / \"memory\" / \"skill_update_check.json\"\n    out.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with open(out, \"w\") as f:\n        json.dump(results, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    print(f\"\\n📄 已保存: {out}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776562949045}}
