ZUBCFyvpJf0m13NRcRFwNW4U84CvyVz-soM9vIrs733t17DoIRFAhiv6wzjKOrw-AvyittR2thmP1K08xpVeld-JPH8quH9q2dd-AW2UQG_iXYKaOX0qbA47F7D_Dn7Ui8yYHNFFZtEfpR5-Xy4JOSsqzPMshJGOPdFXRnX0DBZsy8QUV8_oMvf6x4VcNw3m5m4P7XLd1iJycch-eO5zxbtADhNcmpxl21AQ4eHYvXT5hbMizYgi6fBfvrUh-j82MptsxNm3lg7D61Y4C8HDYPF5C2aW6Zk2PdvfjBIUYlJJrkaWk94G307BK-sj2X7kGK20MSZux__jJSyneJC9kn-fVWhXFHF2ef3CklFIGp-dbu893cr9w9RkABq3fPCec-wFBlLxXlRR04TJnF62HZClxIP9CRncI8C4iD5Zal6BRcecdaKATSTUNa7SggM_rC4AMYZFfCJcj0u5WvryDu_H5OucnWTEft1jb9LjsnYlXXGe2DPXqm3bbBYt5dEm_PYkB8DNCKWUryzUaTdlvZGL9QWGcxjWXX3q8VX38uj5gDntl-dcga8NI2b9UR7pXKax3hyxBu88xohEPTeSleH_G-qgrmO1oy0CTMBCeBGKeHL1Ybj1YuDZ8pMxi0zBJG_n2typwlTI6Hd4JEn_FlqyhNcxX9MquScBhl1S0RXDgXADz0JQPffmwKlj7bUw7w==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering update script**\\n\\nI'm thinking about an update command that could be useful for preflight checks. If a skill seems suspicious, I might want to skip it. I'll test the built-in skill-creator, but I need to keep in mind that it might not involve local changes, since it's built-in, not within the clawhub directory. I should implement a script to load the clawhub list, resolve actual paths, and manage updates accordingly, while noting any local skills that necessitate review.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering OpenClaw version check**\\n\\nI’m thinking about incorporating a version check into another script, but the current cron prompt already handles the OpenClaw version separately. Maybe the prompt itself has the wrong npm package. I should update the cron prompt to use `npm show openclaw version` and have it call the script with `--auto-update-safe`. It might be simpler to update the prompt instead of adding complexity to the script, although I might still want to allow `--check-openclaw` in the script for flexibility.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Editing the script for skill management**\\n\\nI'm planning to edit the script to handle additional arguments like `--auto-update-safe` and `--json-out`, which I will default to false. I need to classify candidate roots based on the filesystem. For each clawhub record, I’ll resolve the path and evaluate its status. If it's found nowhere, it'll be marked as missing. Skills in built-in, external, or local paths that aren't clawhub-managed will be noted as available. I'll also gather local-only skills and ensure they’re not misclassified due to directory types.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating update mechanisms**\\n\\nI’m thinking about how to handle updates for the script. If the system indicates \\\"already up to date,\\\" we won’t proceed with an update. But if it shows it has been \\\"updated\\\" or \\\"installed,\\\" I need to ensure clarity regarding local changes. The user desires an auto-update feature if it's worthwhile, so I’ll include a mechanism for that. If ClawHub confirms a hash match, it will update automatically, which seems reasonable!\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Refining update checks**\\n\\nI'm considering how the hash algorithm might involve metadata or differ from manual edits in local files, which could lead to skips in safe autoupdates. I want to fix the report to clarify which updates are worth it. For files managed by ClawHub, we might need to check for the latest version. I'll think about integrating an OpenClaw version check into the script to prevent any mismanagement from cron prompts. Adding a function to check the OpenClaw version seems straightforward!\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Simplifying script and output**\\n\\nI think it’s a great idea to have the cron prompt run the script and deliver the output directly, simplifying the process. I want to make the script comprehensive, checking both skills and OpenClaw versions, so the cron job only runs one script. The user might be expressing concerns about the GitHub update checker rather than wanting daily auto-checks, but this improvement is still useful. I could rename the output header to \\\"自动更新检查\\\" and will ensure we include the OpenClaw version in the JSON output. Time to write the script and test it!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_11qmGBRVWrgiD5OWcUdw0HRX|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4345bf6dc819a9d160ba83a389394","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSkill / OpenClaw Update Checker v5\n\n目标：\n1. 不再只盯 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills，改为扫描实际存在的多个 skills 根目录\n2. 明确区分：ClawHub 托管 / 本地自定义 / 扩展技能 / 内置技能 / ACP 技能 / 缺失记录\n3. 对 ClawHub 托管技能支持“安全自动更新”：直接调用 `clawhub update <slug>`\n   - 若本地 hash 不匹配 → 视为本地变更，保留本地\n   - 若被标记 suspicious → 不自动更新\n   - 若已是最新 → 明确说明\n   - 若成功升级 → 明确列出\n4. OpenClaw 版本检查改为检查 `openclaw` 包，而不是误查 `clawhub`\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport json\nimport os\nimport re\nimport shutil\nimport subprocess\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nHOME = Path.home()\nWORKSPACE = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nOUTPUT_JSON = WORKSPACE / \"memory\" / \"skill_update_check.json\"\n\nRISK_PATTERNS = [\n    \"eval(\",\n    \"exec(\",\n    \"subprocess.\",\n    \"os.system(\",\n    \"shell=True\",\n    \"requests.\",\n    \"httpx.\",\n    \"socket.\",\n    \"cryptography\",\n    \"Crypto.\",\n]\n\nROOT_SPECS = [\n    (HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\" / \"skills\", \"clawhub\"),\n    (HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"skills\", \"local\"),\n    (HOME / \".agents\" / \"skills\", \"agent-local\"),\n    (HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"extensions\" / \"openclaw-lark\" / \"skills\", \"extension\"),\n]\nGLOB_ROOT_SPECS = [\n    (\n        HOME\n        / \"Library\"\n        / \"pnpm\"\n        / \"global\"\n        / \"5\"\n        / \".pnpm\"\n        / \"openclaw@*\"\n        / \"node_modules\"\n        / \"openclaw\"\n        / \"skills\",\n        \"builtin\",\n    ),\n    (\n        HOME\n        / \"Library\"\n        / \"pnpm\"\n        / \"global\"\n        / \"5\"\n        / \".pnpm\"\n        / \"openclaw@*\"\n        / \"node_modules\"\n        / \"openclaw\"\n        / \"dist\"\n        / \"extensions\"\n        / \"acpx\"\n        / \"skills\",\n        \"acpx\",\n    ),\n]\n\nROOT_LABELS = {\n    \"clawhub\": \"ClawHub 托管\",\n    \"local\": \"本地技能\",\n    \"agent-local\": \"Agent 本地技能\",\n    \"extension\": \"扩展技能\",\n    \"builtin\": \"OpenClaw 内置\",\n    \"acpx\": \"ACPX 内置\",\n}\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass SkillLocation:\n    path: Path\n    root_kind: str\n\n\ndef run_cmd(cmd: list[str], timeout: int = 60, cwd: Path | None = None) -> tuple[str, str, int]:\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            cmd,\n            capture_output=True,\n            text=True,\n            timeout=timeout,\n            cwd=str(cwd) if cwd else None,\n        )\n        return result.stdout.strip(), result.stderr.strip(), result.returncode\n    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired as exc:\n        return exc.stdout or \"\", exc.stderr or f\"timeout after {timeout}s\", -1\n    except FileNotFoundError as exc:\n        return \"\", str(exc), 127\n    except Exception as exc:  # pragma: no cover\n        return \"\", str(exc), -1\n\n\ndef iter_skill_roots() -> list[tuple[Path, str]]:\n    roots: list[tuple[Path, str]] = []\n    seen: set[Path] = set()\n    for path, kind in ROOT_SPECS:\n        if path.exists() and path.is_dir() and path not in seen:\n            roots.append((path, kind))\n            seen.add(path)\n    for pattern, kind in GLOB_ROOT_SPECS:\n        for path in sorted(Path().glob(str(pattern))):\n            if path.exists() and path.is_dir() and path not in seen:\n                roots.append((path, kind))\n                seen.add(path)\n    return roots\n\n\ndef list_skill_dirs(root: Path) -> list[Path]:\n    result: list[Path] = []\n    if not root.exists():\n        return result\n    for item in sorted(root.iterdir()):\n        if not item.is_dir():\n            continue\n        if item.name in {\"dist\", \"memory\", \"__pycache__\", \"node_modules\"}:\n            continue\n        if (item / \"SKILL.md\").exists():\n            result.append(item)\n    return result\n\n\ndef resolve_skill(name: str, roots: list[tuple[Path, str]]) -> SkillLocation | None:\n    for root, kind in roots:\n        candidate = root / name\n        if candidate.is_dir() and (candidate / \"SKILL.md\").exists():\n            return SkillLocation(candidate, kind)\n    return None\n\n\ndef gather_local_only_skills(clawhub_names: set[str], roots: list[tuple[Path, str]]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    items: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    seen: set[str] = set()\n    for root, kind in roots:\n        for skill_dir in list_skill_dirs(root):\n            name = skill_dir.name\n            if name in clawhub_names or name in seen:\n                continue\n            seen.add(name)\n            items.append(\n                {\n                    \"name\": name,\n                    \"source\": kind,\n                    \"source_label\": ROOT_LABELS.get(kind, kind),\n                    \"path\": str(skill_dir),\n                    \"type\": \"local_only\",\n                }\n            )\n    return sorted(items, key=lambda x: (x[\"source_label\"], x[\"name\"]))\n\n\ndef get_installed_clawhub_skills() -> list[dict[str, str]]:\n    stdout, stderr, rc = run_cmd([\"clawhub\", \"list\"], timeout=30)\n    if rc != 0:\n        return []\n    skills: list[dict[str, str]] = []\n    for line in stdout.splitlines():\n        parts = line.strip().split()\n        if len(parts) >= 2:\n            skills.append({\"name\": parts[0], \"version\": parts[1]})\n    return skills\n\n\ndef scan_risk(skill_path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    code_files: list[str] = []\n    hits: list[str] = []\n    for file in skill_path.rglob(\"*\"):\n        if not file.is_file():\n            continue\n        if any(part in {\".git\", \"node_modules\", \"__pycache__\"} for part in file.parts):\n            continue\n        if file.suffix.lower() not in {\".py\", \".js\", \".sh\", \".ts\"}:\n            continue\n        rel = str(file.relative_to(skill_path))\n        code_files.append(rel)\n        try:\n            content = file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\", errors=\"ignore\")[:20000]\n        except Exception:\n            continue\n        for pattern in RISK_PATTERNS:\n            if pattern in content:\n                hits.append(f\"{rel}:{pattern}\")\n                if len(hits) >= 5:\n                    break\n        if len(hits) >= 5:\n            break\n    return {\"code_count\": len(code_files), \"risk_hits\": hits}\n\n\ndef read_clawhub_origin(skill_path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    origin = skill_path / \".clawhub\" / \"origin.json\"\n    if not origin.exists():\n        return {}\n    try:\n        return json.loads(origin.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    except Exception:\n        return {}\n\n\ndef parse_clawhub_update_output(name: str, output: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    text = (output or \"\").strip()\n    lower = text.lower()\n    if not text:\n        return {\n            \"update_status\": \"unknown\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"🔍 需人工确认\",\n            \"reason\": \"clawhub 无输出\",\n            \"updated\": False,\n        }\n    if \"local changes (no match)\" in lower:\n        return {\n            \"update_status\": \"local_changes\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"✅ 保留本地\",\n            \"reason\": \"ClawHub 判定本地内容已偏离已发布版本，自动更新已跳过\",\n            \"updated\": False,\n        }\n    if \"skipped (use --force to update suspicious skills)\" in lower or \"flagged as suspicious\" in lower:\n        return {\n            \"update_status\": \"suspicious\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⚠️ 需review\",\n            \"reason\": \"被 ClawHub 标记为 suspicious，未自动覆盖\",\n            \"updated\": False,\n        }\n    if \"already up to date\" in lower or \"up-to-date\" in lower or \"already latest\" in lower:\n        return {\n            \"update_status\": \"up_to_date\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"✅ 已是最新\",\n            \"reason\": \"已是最新版本\",\n            \"updated\": False,\n        }\n    if f\"- checking {name}\".lower() in lower and (\"updated\" in lower or \"installed\" in lower or \"latest\" in lower):\n        return {\n            \"update_status\": \"updated\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"🚀 已自动更新\",\n            \"reason\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\n            \"updated\": True,\n        }\n    if \"error\" in lower or \"failed\" in lower:\n        return {\n            \"update_status\": \"error\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⚠️ 更新失败\",\n            \"reason\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\n            \"updated\": False,\n        }\n    return {\n        \"update_status\": \"unknown\",\n        \"recommendation\": \"🔍 需人工确认\",\n        \"reason\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\n        \"updated\": False,\n    }\n\n\ndef evaluate_clawhub_skill(\n    item: dict[str, str],\n    roots: list[tuple[Path, str]],\n    auto_update_safe: bool,\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    name = item[\"name\"]\n    version = item[\"version\"]\n    loc = resolve_skill(name, roots)\n    if not loc:\n        return {\n            \"name\": name,\n            \"version\": version,\n            \"installed\": False,\n            \"status\": \"missing\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⏭ 记录存在但本地缺失\",\n            \"reason\": \"clawhub list 有记录，但在实际技能目录未找到\",\n            \"source\": \"missing\",\n            \"source_label\": \"缺失\",\n        }\n\n    risk = scan_risk(loc.path)\n    origin = read_clawhub_origin(loc.path)\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"name\": name,\n        \"version\": version,\n        \"installed\": True,\n        \"path\": str(loc.path),\n        \"source\": loc.root_kind,\n        \"source_label\": ROOT_LABELS.get(loc.root_kind, loc.root_kind),\n        \"code_count\": risk[\"code_count\"],\n        \"risk_hits\": risk[\"risk_hits\"],\n        \"clawhub_origin\": origin,\n    }\n\n    # 不是 ClawHub 托管目录，但本地可用：不能再报“未安装”\n    if loc.root_kind != \"clawhub\":\n        result.update(\n            {\n                \"status\": \"available_non_clawhub\",\n                \"recommendation\": f\"✅ 已安装（{ROOT_LABELS.get(loc.root_kind, loc.root_kind)}）\",\n                \"reason\": \"本地可用，但不在 ClawHub 托管目录；不应标记为未安装\",\n            }\n        )\n        return result\n\n    # ClawHub 托管目录\n    if risk[\"risk_hits\"]:\n        result.update(\n            {\n                \"status\": \"managed_review\",\n                \"recommendation\": \"⚠️ 需review\",\n                \"reason\": f\"检测到敏感模式：{risk['risk_hits'][0]}\",\n            }\n        )\n        return result\n\n    if auto_update_safe:\n        stdout, stderr, rc = run_cmd([\"clawhub\", \"update\", name], timeout=120, cwd=WORKSPACE)\n        parsed = parse_clawhub_update_output(name, \"\\n\".join([stdout, stderr]).strip())\n        result.update(parsed)\n        result[\"update_stdout\"] = stdout\n        result[\"update_stderr\"] = stderr\n        result[\"update_rc\"] = rc\n        result[\"status\"] = parsed[\"update_status\"]\n    else:\n        result.update(\n            {\n                \"status\": \"managed_detected\",\n                \"recommendation\": \"🔄 可自动检查\",\n                \"reason\": \"ClawHub 托管技能，可在安全模式下执行自动更新\",\n            }\n        )\n    return result\n\n\ndef check_openclaw_version() -> dict[str, Any]:\n    current_out, current_err, _ = run_cmd([\"openclaw\", \"--version\"], timeout=20)\n    latest_out, latest_err, _ = run_cmd([\"npm\", \"show\", \"openclaw\", \"version\"], timeout=30)\n    current = (current_out or current_err).strip().splitlines()[0] if (current_out or current_err).strip() else \"unknown\"\n    latest = (latest_out or latest_err).strip().splitlines()[0] if (latest_out or latest_err).strip() else \"unknown\"\n    current_version_match = re.search(r\"(\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+)\", current)\n    latest_version_match = re.search(r\"(\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+)\", latest)\n    current_version = current_version_match.group(1) if current_version_match else current\n    latest_version = latest_version_match.group(1) if latest_version_match else latest\n    needs_update = current_version != \"unknown\" and latest_version != \"unknown\" and current_version != latest_version\n    return {\n        \"current\": current_version,\n        \"latest\": latest_version,\n        \"needs_update\": needs_update,\n        \"raw_current\": current,\n        \"raw_latest\": latest,\n    }\n\n\ndef print_summary(results: list[dict[str, Any]], local_only: list[dict[str, Any]], version_info: dict[str, Any], auto_update_safe: bool) -> None:\n    updated = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") == \"updated\"]\n    up_to_date = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") == \"up_to_date\"]\n    keep_local = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") in {\"local_changes\", \"available_non_clawhub\"}]\n    review = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") in {\"managed_review\", \"suspicious\", \"error\", \"unknown\"}]\n    missing = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") == \"missing\"]\n\n    print(\"=\" * 72)\n    print(\"🔍 Skill / OpenClaw 更新检查 v5\")\n    print(\"=\" * 72)\n    print(f\"\\n📦 ClawHub 记录: {len(results)} 个\")\n    print(f\"📚 本地额外技能: {len(local_only)} 个\")\n    print(f\"🤖 自动更新模式: {'开启' if auto_update_safe else '关闭'}\")\n\n    print(\"\\n一、ClawHub 记录技能\")\n    print(\"┌\" + \"─\" * 70 + \"┐\")\n    print(f\"│ {'Skill':<28} {'来源':<14} {'结论':<24} │\")\n    print(\"├\" + \"─\" * 70 + \"┤\")\n    for r in results:\n        name = r[\"name\"][:28]\n        source = r.get(\"source_label\", \"-\")[:14]\n        rec = r.get(\"recommendation\", \"-\")[:24]\n        print(f\"│ {name:<28} {source:<14} {rec:<24} │\")\n    print(\"└\" + \"─\" * 70 + \"┘\")\n\n    if updated:\n        print(f\"\\n🚀 已自动更新（{len(updated)} 个）：\")\n        for r in updated:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if up_to_date:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 已是最新（{len(up_to_date)} 个）：\")\n        print(\"  • \" + \"、\".join(r[\"name\"] for r in up_to_date))\n\n    if keep_local:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 保留本地（{len(keep_local)} 个）：\")\n        for r in keep_local:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if review:\n        print(f\"\\n⚠️ 需 review（{len(review)} 个）：\")\n        for r in review:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if missing:\n        print(f\"\\n⏭ 记录漂移 / 缺失（{len(missing)} 个）：\")\n        for r in missing:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if local_only:\n        print(f\"\\n二、本地可用但不受 ClawHub 托管的技能（{len(local_only)} 个）\")\n        for item in local_only:\n            print(f\"  • {item['name']} [{item['source_label']}]\")\n\n    print(\"\\n三、OpenClaw 版本\")\n    if version_info.get(\"needs_update\"):\n        print(f\"  • 当前: {version_info['current']} | 最新: {version_info['latest']} | 建议升级 OpenClaw\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  • 当前: {version_info['current']} | 最新: {version_info['latest']} | 已同步\")\n\n    print(\"\\n四、结论\")\n    if updated:\n        print(f\"  • 已自动更新 {len(updated)} 个安全技能。\")\n    else:\n        print(\"  • 本轮没有成功自动更新的技能。\")\n    print(\"  • 不再把内置 / 扩展 / 本地技能误报为“未安装”。\")\n    if missing:\n        print(\"  • 存在 clawhub 记录漂移，建议后续清理无效记录或重装缺失项。\")\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Check skills across real roots and auto-update safe ClawHub skills\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--auto-update-safe\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"run `clawhub update <slug>` for ClawHub-managed skills\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    roots = iter_skill_roots()\n    clawhub_skills = get_installed_clawhub_skills()\n    clawhub_names = {item[\"name\"] for item in clawhub_skills}\n\n    results = [evaluate_clawhub_skill(item, roots, auto_update_safe=args.auto_update_safe) for item in clawhub_skills]\n    local_only = gather_local_only_skills(clawhub_names, roots)\n    version_info = check_openclaw_version()\n\n    payload = {\n        \"checked_at\": __import__(\"datetime\").datetime.now().isoformat(),\n        \"auto_update_safe\": args.auto_update_safe,\n        \"roots\": [{\"path\": str(path), \"kind\": kind, \"label\": ROOT_LABELS.get(kind, kind)} for path, kind in roots],\n        \"clawhub_results\": results,\n        \"local_only\": local_only,\n        \"openclaw\": version_info,\n    }\n    OUTPUT_JSON.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    OUTPUT_JSON.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + \"\\n\", encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    print_summary(results, local_only, version_info, args.auto_update_safe)\n    print(f\"\\n📄 已保存: {OUTPUT_JSON}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py\",\"content\":\"#!/usr/bin/env python3\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nSkill / OpenClaw Update Checker v5\\n\\n目标：\\n1. 不再只盯 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills，改为扫描实际存在的多个 skills 根目录\\n2. 明确区分：ClawHub 托管 / 本地自定义 / 扩展技能 / 内置技能 / ACP 技能 / 缺失记录\\n3. 对 ClawHub 托管技能支持“安全自动更新”：直接调用 `clawhub update <slug>`\\n   - 若本地 hash 不匹配 → 视为本地变更，保留本地\\n   - 若被标记 suspicious → 不自动更新\\n   - 若已是最新 → 明确说明\\n   - 若成功升级 → 明确列出\\n4. OpenClaw 版本检查改为检查 `openclaw` 包，而不是误查 `clawhub`\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport argparse\\nimport json\\nimport os\\nimport re\\nimport shutil\\nimport subprocess\\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nfrom typing import Any\\n\\nHOME = Path.home()\\nWORKSPACE = HOME / \\\".openclaw\\\" / \\\"workspace\\\"\\nOUTPUT_JSON = WORKSPACE / \\\"memory\\\" / \\\"skill_update_check.json\\\"\\n\\nRISK_PATTERNS = [\\n    \\\"eval(\\\",\\n    \\\"exec(\\\",\\n    \\\"subprocess.\\\",\\n    \\\"os.system(\\\",\\n    \\\"shell=True\\\",\\n    \\\"requests.\\\",\\n    \\\"httpx.\\\",\\n    \\\"socket.\\\",\\n    \\\"cryptography\\\",\\n    \\\"Crypto.\\\",\\n]\\n\\nROOT_SPECS = [\\n    (HOME / \\\".openclaw\\\" / \\\"workspace\\\" / \\\"skills\\\", \\\"clawhub\\\"),\\n    (HOME / \\\".openclaw\\\" / \\\"skills\\\", \\\"local\\\"),\\n    (HOME / \\\".agents\\\" / \\\"skills\\\", \\\"agent-local\\\"),\\n    (HOME / \\\".openclaw\\\" / \\\"extensions\\\" / \\\"openclaw-lark\\\" / \\\"skills\\\", \\\"extension\\\"),\\n]\\nGLOB_ROOT_SPECS = [\\n    (\\n        HOME\\n        / \\\"Library\\\"\\n        / \\\"pnpm\\\"\\n        / \\\"global\\\"\\n        / \\\"5\\\"\\n        / \\\".pnpm\\\"\\n        / \\\"openclaw@*\\\"\\n        / \\\"node_modules\\\"\\n        / \\\"openclaw\\\"\\n        / \\\"skills\\\",\\n        \\\"builtin\\\",\\n    ),\\n    (\\n        HOME\\n        / \\\"Library\\\"\\n        / \\\"pnpm\\\"\\n        / \\\"global\\\"\\n        / \\\"5\\\"\\n        / \\\".pnpm\\\"\\n        / \\\"openclaw@*\\\"\\n        / \\\"node_modules\\\"\\n        / \\\"openclaw\\\"\\n        / \\\"dist\\\"\\n        / \\\"extensions\\\"\\n        / \\\"acpx\\\"\\n        / \\\"skills\\\",\\n        \\\"acpx\\\",\\n    ),\\n]\\n\\nROOT_LABELS = {\\n    \\\"clawhub\\\": \\\"ClawHub 托管\\\",\\n    \\\"local\\\": \\\"本地技能\\\",\\n    \\\"agent-local\\\": \\\"Agent 本地技能\\\",\\n    \\\"extension\\\": \\\"扩展技能\\\",\\n    \\\"builtin\\\": \\\"OpenClaw 内置\\\",\\n    \\\"acpx\\\": \\\"ACPX 内置\\\",\\n}\\n\\n\\n@dataclass\\nclass SkillLocation:\\n    path: Path\\n    root_kind: str\\n\\n\\ndef run_cmd(cmd: list[str], timeout: int = 60, cwd: Path | None = None) -> tuple[str, str, int]:\\n    try:\\n        result = subprocess.run(\\n            cmd,\\n            capture_output=True,\\n            text=True,\\n            timeout=timeout,\\n            cwd=str(cwd) if cwd else None,\\n        )\\n        return result.stdout.strip(), result.stderr.strip(), result.returncode\\n    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired as exc:\\n        return exc.stdout or \\\"\\\", exc.stderr or f\\\"timeout after {timeout}s\\\", -1\\n    except FileNotFoundError as exc:\\n        return \\\"\\\", str(exc), 127\\n    except Exception as exc:  # pragma: no cover\\n        return \\\"\\\", str(exc), -1\\n\\n\\ndef iter_skill_roots() -> list[tuple[Path, str]]:\\n    roots: list[tuple[Path, str]] = []\\n    seen: set[Path] = set()\\n    for path, kind in ROOT_SPECS:\\n        if path.exists() and path.is_dir() and path not in seen:\\n            roots.append((path, kind))\\n            seen.add(path)\\n    for pattern, kind in GLOB_ROOT_SPECS:\\n        for path in sorted(Path().glob(str(pattern))):\\n            if path.exists() and path.is_dir() and path not in seen:\\n                roots.append((path, kind))\\n                seen.add(path)\\n    return roots\\n\\n\\ndef list_skill_dirs(root: Path) -> list[Path]:\\n    result: list[Path] = []\\n    if not root.exists():\\n        return result\\n    for item in sorted(root.iterdir()):\\n        if not item.is_dir():\\n            continue\\n        if item.name in {\\\"dist\\\", \\\"memory\\\", \\\"__pycache__\\\", \\\"node_modules\\\"}:\\n            continue\\n        if (item / \\\"SKILL.md\\\").exists():\\n            result.append(item)\\n    return result\\n\\n\\ndef resolve_skill(name: str, roots: list[tuple[Path, str]]) -> SkillLocation | None:\\n    for root, kind in roots:\\n        candidate = root / name\\n        if candidate.is_dir() and (candidate / \\\"SKILL.md\\\").exists():\\n            return SkillLocation(candidate, kind)\\n    return None\\n\\n\\ndef gather_local_only_skills(clawhub_names: set[str], roots: list[tuple[Path, str]]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\\n    items: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\\n    seen: set[str] = set()\\n    for root, kind in roots:\\n        for skill_dir in list_skill_dirs(root):\\n            name = skill_dir.name\\n            if name in clawhub_names or name in seen:\\n                continue\\n            seen.add(name)\\n            items.append(\\n                {\\n                    \\\"name\\\": name,\\n                    \\\"source\\\": kind,\\n                    \\\"source_label\\\": ROOT_LABELS.get(kind, kind),\\n                    \\\"path\\\": str(skill_dir),\\n                    \\\"type\\\": \\\"local_only\\\",\\n                }\\n            )\\n    return sorted(items, key=lambda x: (x[\\\"source_label\\\"], x[\\\"name\\\"]))\\n\\n\\ndef get_installed_clawhub_skills() -> list[dict[str, str]]:\\n    stdout, stderr, rc = run_cmd([\\\"clawhub\\\", \\\"list\\\"], timeout=30)\\n    if rc != 0:\\n        return []\\n    skills: list[dict[str, str]] = []\\n    for line in stdout.splitlines():\\n        parts = line.strip().split()\\n        if len(parts) >= 2:\\n            skills.append({\\\"name\\\": parts[0], \\\"version\\\": parts[1]})\\n    return skills\\n\\n\\ndef scan_risk(skill_path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    code_files: list[str] = []\\n    hits: list[str] = []\\n    for file in skill_path.rglob(\\\"*\\\"):\\n        if not file.is_file():\\n            continue\\n        if any(part in {\\\".git\\\", \\\"node_modules\\\", \\\"__pycache__\\\"} for part in file.parts):\\n            continue\\n        if file.suffix.lower() not in {\\\".py\\\", \\\".js\\\", \\\".sh\\\", \\\".ts\\\"}:\\n            continue\\n        rel = str(file.relative_to(skill_path))\\n        code_files.append(rel)\\n        try:\\n            content = file.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\", errors=\\\"ignore\\\")[:20000]\\n        except Exception:\\n            continue\\n        for pattern in RISK_PATTERNS:\\n            if pattern in content:\\n                hits.append(f\\\"{rel}:{pattern}\\\")\\n                if len(hits) >= 5:\\n                    break\\n        if len(hits) >= 5:\\n            break\\n    return {\\\"code_count\\\": len(code_files), \\\"risk_hits\\\": hits}\\n\\n\\ndef read_clawhub_origin(skill_path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    origin = skill_path / \\\".clawhub\\\" / \\\"origin.json\\\"\\n    if not origin.exists():\\n        return {}\\n    try:\\n        return json.loads(origin.read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\"))\\n    except Exception:\\n        return {}\\n\\n\\ndef parse_clawhub_update_output(name: str, output: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    text = (output or \\\"\\\").strip()\\n    lower = text.lower()\\n    if not text:\\n        return {\\n            \\\"update_status\\\": \\\"unknown\\\",\\n            \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"🔍 需人工确认\\\",\\n            \\\"reason\\\": \\\"clawhub 无输出\\\",\\n            \\\"updated\\\": False,\\n        }\\n    if \\\"local changes (no match)\\\" in lower:\\n        return {\\n            \\\"update_status\\\": \\\"local_changes\\\",\\n            \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"✅ 保留本地\\\",\\n            \\\"reason\\\": \\\"ClawHub 判定本地内容已偏离已发布版本，自动更新已跳过\\\",\\n            \\\"updated\\\": False,\\n        }\\n    if \\\"skipped (use --force to update suspicious skills)\\\" in lower or \\\"flagged as suspicious\\\" in lower:\\n        return {\\n            \\\"update_status\\\": \\\"suspicious\\\",\\n            \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"⚠️ 需review\\\",\\n            \\\"reason\\\": \\\"被 ClawHub 标记为 suspicious，未自动覆盖\\\",\\n            \\\"updated\\\": False,\\n        }\\n    if \\\"already up to date\\\" in lower or \\\"up-to-date\\\" in lower or \\\"already latest\\\" in lower:\\n        return {\\n            \\\"update_status\\\": \\\"up_to_date\\\",\\n            \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"✅ 已是最新\\\",\\n            \\\"reason\\\": \\\"已是最新版本\\\",\\n            \\\"updated\\\": False,\\n        }\\n    if f\\\"- checking {name}\\\".lower() in lower and (\\\"updated\\\" in lower or \\\"installed\\\" in lower or \\\"latest\\\" in lower):\\n        return {\\n            \\\"update_status\\\": \\\"updated\\\",\\n            \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"🚀 已自动更新\\\",\\n            \\\"reason\\\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\\n            \\\"updated\\\": True,\\n        }\\n    if \\\"error\\\" in lower or \\\"failed\\\" in lower:\\n        return {\\n            \\\"update_status\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n            \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"⚠️ 更新失败\\\",\\n            \\\"reason\\\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\\n            \\\"updated\\\": False,\\n        }\\n    return {\\n        \\\"update_status\\\": \\\"unknown\\\",\\n        \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"🔍 需人工确认\\\",\\n        \\\"reason\\\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\\n        \\\"updated\\\": False,\\n    }\\n\\n\\ndef evaluate_clawhub_skill(\\n    item: dict[str, str],\\n    roots: list[tuple[Path, str]],\\n    auto_update_safe: bool,\\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    name = item[\\\"name\\\"]\\n    version = item[\\\"version\\\"]\\n    loc = resolve_skill(name, roots)\\n    if not loc:\\n        return {\\n            \\\"name\\\": name,\\n            \\\"version\\\": version,\\n            \\\"installed\\\": False,\\n            \\\"status\\\": \\\"missing\\\",\\n            \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"⏭ 记录存在但本地缺失\\\",\\n            \\\"reason\\\": \\\"clawhub list 有记录，但在实际技能目录未找到\\\",\\n            \\\"source\\\": \\\"missing\\\",\\n            \\\"source_label\\\": \\\"缺失\\\",\\n        }\\n\\n    risk = scan_risk(loc.path)\\n    origin = read_clawhub_origin(loc.path)\\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\\n        \\\"name\\\": name,\\n        \\\"version\\\": version,\\n        \\\"installed\\\": True,\\n        \\\"path\\\": str(loc.path),\\n        \\\"source\\\": loc.root_kind,\\n        \\\"source_label\\\": ROOT_LABELS.get(loc.root_kind, loc.root_kind),\\n        \\\"code_count\\\": risk[\\\"code_count\\\"],\\n        \\\"risk_hits\\\": risk[\\\"risk_hits\\\"],\\n        \\\"clawhub_origin\\\": origin,\\n    }\\n\\n    # 不是 ClawHub 托管目录，但本地可用：不能再报“未安装”\\n    if loc.root_kind != \\\"clawhub\\\":\\n        result.update(\\n            {\\n                \\\"status\\\": \\\"available_non_clawhub\\\",\\n                \\\"recommendation\\\": f\\\"✅ 已安装（{ROOT_LABELS.get(loc.root_kind, loc.root_kind)}）\\\",\\n                \\\"reason\\\": \\\"本地可用，但不在 ClawHub 托管目录；不应标记为未安装\\\",\\n            }\\n        )\\n        return result\\n\\n    # ClawHub 托管目录\\n    if risk[\\\"risk_hits\\\"]:\\n        result.update(\\n            {\\n                \\\"status\\\": \\\"managed_review\\\",\\n                \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"⚠️ 需review\\\",\\n                \\\"reason\\\": f\\\"检测到敏感模式：{risk['risk_hits'][0]}\\\",\\n            }\\n        )\\n        return result\\n\\n    if auto_update_safe:\\n        stdout, stderr, rc = run_cmd([\\\"clawhub\\\", \\\"update\\\", name], timeout=120, cwd=WORKSPACE)\\n        parsed = parse_clawhub_update_output(name, \\\"\\\\n\\\".join([stdout, stderr]).strip())\\n        result.update(parsed)\\n        result[\\\"update_stdout\\\"] = stdout\\n        result[\\\"update_stderr\\\"] = stderr\\n        result[\\\"update_rc\\\"] = rc\\n        result[\\\"status\\\"] = parsed[\\\"update_status\\\"]\\n    else:\\n        result.update(\\n            {\\n                \\\"status\\\": \\\"managed_detected\\\",\\n                \\\"recommendation\\\": \\\"🔄 可自动检查\\\",\\n                \\\"reason\\\": \\\"ClawHub 托管技能，可在安全模式下执行自动更新\\\",\\n            }\\n        )\\n    return result\\n\\n\\ndef check_openclaw_version() -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    current_out, current_err, _ = run_cmd([\\\"openclaw\\\", \\\"--version\\\"], timeout=20)\\n    latest_out, latest_err, _ = run_cmd([\\\"npm\\\", \\\"show\\\", \\\"openclaw\\\", \\\"version\\\"], timeout=30)\\n    current = (current_out or current_err).strip().splitlines()[0] if (current_out or current_err).strip() else \\\"unknown\\\"\\n    latest = (latest_out or latest_err).strip().splitlines()[0] if (latest_out or latest_err).strip() else \\\"unknown\\\"\\n    current_version_match = re.search(r\\\"(\\\\d+\\\\.\\\\d+\\\\.\\\\d+)\\\", current)\\n    latest_version_match = re.search(r\\\"(\\\\d+\\\\.\\\\d+\\\\.\\\\d+)\\\", latest)\\n    current_version = current_version_match.group(1) if current_version_match else current\\n    latest_version = latest_version_match.group(1) if latest_version_match else latest\\n    needs_update = current_version != \\\"unknown\\\" and latest_version != \\\"unknown\\\" and current_version != latest_version\\n    return {\\n        \\\"current\\\": current_version,\\n        \\\"latest\\\": latest_version,\\n        \\\"needs_update\\\": needs_update,\\n        \\\"raw_current\\\": current,\\n        \\\"raw_latest\\\": latest,\\n    }\\n\\n\\ndef print_summary(results: list[dict[str, Any]], local_only: list[dict[str, Any]], version_info: dict[str, Any], auto_update_safe: bool) -> None:\\n    updated = [r for r in results if r.get(\\\"status\\\") == \\\"updated\\\"]\\n    up_to_date = [r for r in results if r.get(\\\"status\\\") == \\\"up_to_date\\\"]\\n    keep_local = [r for r in results if r.get(\\\"status\\\") in {\\\"local_changes\\\", \\\"available_non_clawhub\\\"}]\\n    review = [r for r in results if r.get(\\\"status\\\") in {\\\"managed_review\\\", \\\"suspicious\\\", \\\"error\\\", \\\"unknown\\\"}]\\n    missing = [r for r in results if r.get(\\\"status\\\") == \\\"missing\\\"]\\n\\n    print(\\\"=\\\" * 72)\\n    print(\\\"🔍 Skill / OpenClaw 更新检查 v5\\\")\\n    print(\\\"=\\\" * 72)\\n    print(f\\\"\\\\n📦 ClawHub 记录: {len(results)} 个\\\")\\n    print(f\\\"📚 本地额外技能: {len(local_only)} 个\\\")\\n    print(f\\\"🤖 自动更新模式: {'开启' if auto_update_safe else '关闭'}\\\")\\n\\n    print(\\\"\\\\n一、ClawHub 记录技能\\\")\\n    print(\\\"┌\\\" + \\\"─\\\" * 70 + \\\"┐\\\")\\n    print(f\\\"│ {'Skill':<28} {'来源':<14} {'结论':<24} │\\\")\\n    print(\\\"├\\\" + \\\"─\\\" * 70 + \\\"┤\\\")\\n    for r in results:\\n        name = r[\\\"name\\\"][:28]\\n        source = r.get(\\\"source_label\\\", \\\"-\\\")[:14]\\n        rec = r.get(\\\"recommendation\\\", \\\"-\\\")[:24]\\n        print(f\\\"│ {name:<28} {source:<14} {rec:<24} │\\\")\\n    print(\\\"└\\\" + \\\"─\\\" * 70 + \\\"┘\\\")\\n\\n    if updated:\\n        print(f\\\"\\\\n🚀 已自动更新（{len(updated)} 个）：\\\")\\n        for r in updated:\\n            print(f\\\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\\\")\\n\\n    if up_to_date:\\n        print(f\\\"\\\\n✅ 已是最新（{len(up_to_date)} 个）：\\\")\\n        print(\\\"  • \\\" + \\\"、\\\".join(r[\\\"name\\\"] for r in up_to_date))\\n\\n    if keep_local:\\n        print(f\\\"\\\\n✅ 保留本地（{len(keep_local)} 个）：\\\")\\n        for r in keep_local:\\n            print(f\\\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\\\")\\n\\n    if review:\\n        print(f\\\"\\\\n⚠️ 需 review（{len(review)} 个）：\\\")\\n        for r in review:\\n            print(f\\\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\\\")\\n\\n    if missing:\\n        print(f\\\"\\\\n⏭ 记录漂移 / 缺失（{len(missing)} 个）：\\\")\\n        for r in missing:\\n            print(f\\\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\\\")\\n\\n    if local_only:\\n        print(f\\\"\\\\n二、本地可用但不受 ClawHub 托管的技能（{len(local_only)} 个）\\\")\\n        for item in local_only:\\n            print(f\\\"  • {item['name']} [{item['source_label']}]\\\")\\n\\n    print(\\\"\\\\n三、OpenClaw 版本\\\")\\n    if version_info.get(\\\"needs_update\\\"):\\n        print(f\\\"  • 当前: {version_info['current']} | 最新: {version_info['latest']} | 建议升级 OpenClaw\\\")\\n    else:\\n        print(f\\\"  • 当前: {version_info['current']} | 最新: {version_info['latest']} | 已同步\\\")\\n\\n    print(\\\"\\\\n四、结论\\\")\\n    if updated:\\n        print(f\\\"  • 已自动更新 {len(updated)} 个安全技能。\\\")\\n    else:\\n        print(\\\"  • 本轮没有成功自动更新的技能。\\\")\\n    print(\\\"  • 不再把内置 / 扩展 / 本地技能误报为“未安装”。\\\")\\n    if missing:\\n        print(\\\"  • 存在 clawhub 记录漂移，建议后续清理无效记录或重装缺失项。\\\")\\n\\n\\ndef main() -> None:\\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\\\"Check skills across real roots and auto-update safe ClawHub skills\\\")\\n    parser.add_argument(\\\"--auto-update-safe\\\", action=\\\"store_true\\\", help=\\\"run `clawhub update <slug>` for ClawHub-managed skills\\\")\\n    args = parser.parse_args()\\n\\n    roots = iter_skill_roots()\\n    clawhub_skills = get_installed_clawhub_skills()\\n    clawhub_names = {item[\\\"name\\\"] for item in clawhub_skills}\\n\\n    results = [evaluate_clawhub_skill(item, roots, auto_update_safe=args.auto_update_safe) for item in clawhub_skills]\\n    local_only = gather_local_only_skills(clawhub_names, roots)\\n    version_info = check_openclaw_version()\\n\\n    payload = {\\n        \\\"checked_at\\\": __import__(\\\"datetime\\\").datetime.now().isoformat(),\\n        \\\"auto_update_safe\\\": args.auto_update_safe,\\n        \\\"roots\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": str(path), \\\"kind\\\": kind, \\\"label\\\": ROOT_LABELS.get(kind, kind)} for path, kind in roots],\\n        \\\"clawhub_results\\\": results,\\n        \\\"local_only\\\": local_only,\\n        \\\"openclaw\\\": version_info,\\n    }\\n    OUTPUT_JSON.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\\n    OUTPUT_JSON.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + \\\"\\\\n\\\", encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\")\\n\\n    print_summary(results, local_only, version_info, args.auto_update_safe)\\n    print(f\\\"\\\\n📄 已保存: {OUTPUT_JSON}\\\")\\n\\n\\nif __name__ == \\\"__main__\\\":\\n    main()\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":938,"output":6523,"cacheRead":209920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":217381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776563257319,"responseId":"resp_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4343b8f2c819ab9a0750a79258047"}}
