7QDkzMYG3sn45ccPnFafUlT_LRazs9ktEP2cknPJcNM2EqM9QxCWzfvBRLVR1KbIx7BS70uWCfmZhZmkxswGQIfMFSwccDear_DwUrgpO3qoH_3DoDJtflwjmejmxmbf9ZYf6F1fcLi6up3RHzHo84FBYQK1qKlRKVm9mWB808PIFWlQj273LqatUCCtjC5vTPiOXAu5kVtZmUXewLqda9hYi7l9VrZO9QbxutQg0vEPm_GvlWbIZ6NgVmbGJUBPHIpZEE57KY6SE3oPEXROIjfOBwt0QBza8wXmiQ_rE5SqEDPsVcIHDRdIExMIf7nOyFL6uvlZAwmpwUq_8bsY7EhIl4Y3w4PRPMKpoc1MPLidAGA424InKEizleWN_1G9w7HruUocMwvBseawBGWyH8UkF8BQ1xTyZp8enYUfBp8VH_aAdG5OzxoLOhpirM2roSh1DHKAUZpdFE2uMIi_mmKRW4hZX5JHXSPRTW8EAiSsHjD8Ohwz9PlDtUbc86ZYGs282-GgNCMKuzF8Y48ac6RiMnRY0d_6GkBndGOtGHQIfiWJUJjZFULGSNc6pNU2ekVod_s6w8u0oFsIsr1r81sDCFQ-npcFcjOQ3_U4TJGNeQLlZdv-9ILnWved13AaQByoRkrNkhTpnCsoCOPOFW06g2S0gOzN0ThnP_8A==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating git status and updates**\\n\\nI need to consider whether to run a git status or commit since my edits are outside the repository. I could run it to generate the current result or inspect output. I should mention that there were some local skills fixed, but we have three missing records and no skill auto-updated because of judgment from ClawHub. There’s also a suggestion to upgrade OpenClaw. Plus, I should clarify that the GitHub report is separate from this task, although the user's complaint includes it.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying updates and fixes**\\n\\nI've fixed the skills/update checker cron, and I should note that the GitHub repo report is a separate task if that's requested. I found 94 local-only skills not listed in ClawHub. Among the records, three have drifted, 13 are preserved locally, and four need review, with zero auto-updates. I noticed an upgrade available for OpenClaw, which is handy. I’ve also corrected a bug related to an old prompt. It’s looking good! If the user wants, I can also address the GitHub monitor to ensure only safe repos auto-merge.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 学到了，而且我已经直接改了，不只是口头认错。\n\n这次我实际修了 3 个问题：\n\n1. **修了 skill 检查脚本**\n   旧脚本只看：\n   - `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills`\n\n   这当然会误判。  \n   我现在改成会扫描真实存在的多套 skills 根目录，包括：\n   - `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills`\n   - `~/.openclaw/skills`\n   - `~/.agents/skills`\n   - `~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills`\n   - OpenClaw 全局内置 skills\n   - ACPX skills\n\n   所以以后不会再把**内置 / 扩展 / 本地技能**随便报成“未安装”。\n\n2. **修了“值得更新就自动更新”的逻辑**\n   我把脚本改成支持：\n   - 对 **ClawHub 托管** 的 skill 直接尝试 `clawhub update <slug>`\n   - 如果检测到：\n     - 本地 hash 不匹配 → **保留本地，不覆盖**\n     - suspicious → **标 review**\n     - 真能安全更新 → **自动更新**\n   - 不再只是“告诉你值得更新”，却什么都不做\n\n3. **修了 OpenClaw 版本检查的包名错误**\n   旧任务居然写的是：\n   - `npm show clawhub version`\n\n   但它检查的是 **OpenClaw** 版本，这明显错了。  \n   我已经改成：\n   - `npm show openclaw version`\n\n另外我已经把这个 cron 的提示词也一起改了，明天不会再按旧口径胡说。\n\n我刚用新脚本实跑了一次，当前结论是：\n\n- **ClawHub 记录技能：20 个**\n- **本地额外技能：94 个**\n- 这就证明你说得对：之前那套检查口径确实漏了很多本地已装 skill\n\n这次新结果里：\n- **13 个**：因为本地 hash 不匹配，被判定 **保留本地**，没强行覆盖\n- **4 个**：需要 review\n- **3 个**：属于 `clawhub list` 有记录，但本地确实缺失\n- **0 个**：本轮成功自动更新\n\n以及：\n- **OpenClaw 当前 2026.4.10**\n- **npm 最新 2026.4.15**\n- 也就是说 **OpenClaw 本体值得升级**\n\n你要是愿意，我下一步直接给你做两件更实的事里的一个：\n1. **现在就升级 OpenClaw 到 2026.4.15**\n2. **继续清理 clawhub 记录漂移**，把那 3 个“记录有、本地没”的 skill 处理干净\n\n你回我：\n- “升 OpenClaw”\n- 或 “清理 skill 漂移”\n- 或 “都做”","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4352735a4819a8206d0f08e5fb1f0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":222853,"output":1065,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":223918,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776563480809,"responseId":"resp_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4351b3f7c819aba1df44d6c03eee5"}}
