y_text\",\"text\":\"**Inspecting package updates**\\n\\nI need to check on the package manager and possibly run a global update for openclaw. It's possible that the openclaw status suggests an update to version 2026.4.15, but it seems the help feature is disabled. I can try running the `openclaw update` command directly. Alternatively, I might consider using `npm i -g openclaw@2026.4.15`, but I need to check if I have the necessary permissions since it's installed globally. I'll look into the current binary path and check the installed version too.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering installation approach**\\n\\nI'm wondering whether I should run installs in parallel or sequentially to avoid running into rate limits. It might be smart to use clawhub to search for each item first, but I need to be cautious with direct installs since they might fail if the slug is absent. Before installing, I should check where clawhub installs items—likely in the workspace or skills directory. I should also consider updating the cron jobs, but maybe it's not necessary now. It seems like I should commit changes after editing scripts.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Addressing OpenClaw upgrade concerns**\\n\\nI’m considering the potential issue of upgrading OpenClaw, wondering if the restart is necessary. It seems manageable, though, since the current agent might keep running despite the package update. I should proceed cautiously, maybe running `openclaw status` after the update to check everything. For cleaning up afterwards, I might need to rerun `skill_update_check` with the auto-update-safe option. I suspect there are about three missing items, and some might get installed in the workspace or skills folders. One built-in skill, `skill-creator`, is already resolved.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我直接开干两件事：先升级 OpenClaw，再把那几个 ClawHub 记录漂移的 skill 补齐/清理，然后回跑一次检查给你看结果。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3ac7b405e714490169e435f2342c819a8700e0b7cf1199b3\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xNXbdmv8MJPTogrocKxgiztx|fc_0b3ac7b405e714490169e435f25b14819ab58687cf33ed485c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\nprintf '%s\\n' '--- current versions ---'\nopenclaw --version || true\nnpm show openclaw version || true\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- current drift targets ---'\npython3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py --auto-update-safe > /tmp/skill_check_before.out 2>&1 || true\ngrep -n \"记录漂移 / 缺失\\|todo-tracker\\|xiaohongshu-mcp\\|stock-daily-analysis\" /tmp/skill_check_before.out || true\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- upgrading OpenClaw ---'\nnpm i -g openclaw@2026.4.15\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- installing missing skills ---'\nclawhub install todo-tracker || true\nclawhub install xiaohongshu-mcp || true\nclawhub install stock-daily-analysis || true\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- rerun check ---'\npython3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py --auto-update-safe > /tmp/skill_check_after.out 2>&1 || true\nsed -n '1,260p' /tmp/skill_check_after.out\nprintf '\\n%s\\n' '--- final versions ---'\nopenclaw --version || true\nnpm show openclaw version || true","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":180,"yieldMs":1000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -e\\nprintf '%s\\\\n' '--- current versions ---'\\nopenclaw --version || true\\nnpm show openclaw version || true\\nprintf '\\\\n%s\\\\n' '--- current drift targets ---'\\npython3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py --auto-update-safe > /tmp/skill_check_before.out 2>&1 || true\\ngrep -n \\\"记录漂移 / 缺失\\\\|todo-tracker\\\\|xiaohongshu-mcp\\\\|stock-daily-analysis\\\" /tmp/skill_check_before.out || true\\nprintf '\\\\n%s\\\\n' '--- upgrading OpenClaw ---'\\nnpm i -g openclaw@2026.4.15\\nprintf '\\\\n%s\\\\n' '--- installing missing skills ---'\\nclawhub install todo-tracker || true\\nclawhub install xiaohongshu-mcp || true\\nclawhub install stock-daily-analysis || true\\npri