pdates status**\\n\\nI should mention that there are 4 review items remaining and 13 local changes skipped. The user wanted updates automatically, but only the 4 need review due to sensitive patterns, while the 13 weren’t updated because Clawhub treated them as local changes. I might suggest forcing specific updates if she prefers that, but I don’t want to overwhelm her with options. It’s also important to note that this task is done since she said, \\\"都做.\\\" I'll keep it straightforward!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 做完了，结果如下。\n\n1. **OpenClaw 已升级**\n- 从 `2026.4.10`\n- 升到 `2026.4.15`\n\n2. **skill 漂移已清理**\n- 我没有强装那 3 个缺失 skill，因为它们都被 ClawHub 标成 **suspicious**\n- 更稳妥的做法是把失效的锁记录从\n  - `~/.openclaw/workspace/.clawhub/lock.json`\n  里清掉\n- 清掉后，`clawhub list` 已经从 **20 个**变成 **17 个**\n- 那 3 个“记录有、本地没”的漂移项已经消失，不再误报\n\n3. **现在的检查结果**\n- **不会再把内置 / 扩展 / 本地技能误报成“未安装”**\n- OpenClaw 版本已经同步到最新\n- 当前没有成功自动更新的 skill，原因也已经被明确分开：\n  - **13 个**：本地内容和已发布版本不匹配，`clawhub` 自动判定为 **保留本地**\n  - **4 个**：需要 review\n    - `memos`\n    - `stock-daily-report`\n    - `xiaohongshu-search-summarizer`\n    - `pua`\n\n4. **你最关心的点，现在已经落地**\n- 值得自动更新的，会自动尝试更新\n- 不能更新的，不再糊里糊涂一句“没安装”打发掉\n- 会明确告诉你：\n  - 已自动更新\n  - 因本地改动跳过\n  - 因风险 review 跳过\n  - 因记录漂移清理掉\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以继续把那 **4 个 review 项**再细分成：\n- **可以强更**\n- **不建议强更**\n- **建议保留本地**\n\n这样这条 03:00 的更新检查就会更接近“能自动就自动，不能自动就讲清楚原因”。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3ac7b405e714490169e43890cbc4819aa830a6540950b9fb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":66170,"output":811,"cacheRead":174848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":241829,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776564350254,"responseId":"resp_0b3ac7b405e714490169e43880e788819aa02a69ec8d57b9c7"}}
