cZI25c3rZ_7-ekEdzPvx9HS57HmoMahuL8yjHPu5WG_X8Ji_t7kU65l4tv2tX6QtQN37yAS2uVDvVlsqB3vwnPENaTt2XZl2iMtGCcYLRdvH0wqjmG2aUibJ2vAYPV6LmGDTUF0k7QkUMgTFM_CVaP_fvD4YtWsYUNKM-LP-PZHKIyXCGTwp1KcdB2f33nKWbi0DyRImJgQYxAYwXZPO6-zbfY2DvM2wpk8NsDO8YXPAj90EJ56tGNL4ryTOKrA5xr7Ee9G9UiTubC5BxDBpk7TrL-tg0lXGnUR9nGu6NiqHxGFljr4WKg4sqFsgu7MAY=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering recommendations**\\n\\nI'm thinking it’s not advisable to recommend preserving something locally unless it’s currently in use and properly configured. I might label it as \\\"建议保留本地\\\" or \\\"不建议强更.\\\" There's also the need to categorize four items into three buckets. I wonder how best to approach that categorization to keep it clear and effective for the user. Let’s see if I can simplify this process!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我分完了。结论很直接：\n\n**可以强更**\n- **暂无**\n\n原因：这 4 个里，没有一个同时满足“上游可解析 + 不可疑 + 不会覆盖本地差异”这三个条件。\n\n**不建议强更**\n- **stock-daily-report**\n  - `schedule_push.py` 里确实有 `subprocess.run(...)`\n  - `clawhub update stock-daily-report` 直接返回 **Skill not found**\n  - 这说明它现在不是一个能稳妥直接覆盖更新的状态，强更风险高，容易把现有推送链路搞坏\n\n- **pua**\n  - `clawhub` 直接把它标成 **suspicious**\n  - 这种我不建议强更，除非你明确要我无视风险强装/强更\n\n**建议保留本地**\n- **memos**\n  - 风险点其实只是它是个正常的 API 客户端，用了 `requests`\n  - 但 `clawhub update memos` 的结果是：**local changes (no match)**\n  - 也就是说本地内容已经和发布版本不一致，强更会直接覆盖当前本地版本  \n  - 结论：**保留本地**\n\n- **xiaohongshu-search-summarizer**\n  - 我检查了你脚本里那个“eval”命中，实际上是 `ast.literal_eval(...)`，不是危险的裸 `eval`\n  - 但 `clawhub update xiaohongshu-search-summarizer` 也是：**local changes (no match)**\n  - 说明它同样不适合直接强更\n  - 结论：**保留本地**\n\n所以最终分桶是：\n\n- **可以强更**：无\n- **不建议强更**：`stock-daily-report`、`pua`\n- **建议保留本地**：`memos`、`xiaohongshu-search-summarizer`\n\n一句话总结：\n这 4 个里，**没有任何一个值得我现在直接强更**。\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续做一层更实用的处理，把这 4 个结果**固化进 03:00 的自动更新检查逻辑**里，变成固定策略：\n- `memos` / `xiaohongshu-search-summarizer` → 默认“保留本地”\n- `stock-daily-report` / `pua` → 默认“不要强更，必须人工确认”\n\n你回我一句 **“固化进去”**，我就直接改。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3ac7b405e714490169e445762590819a8c0f781aab28020e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":248350,"output":1576,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":249926,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776567643878,"responseId":"resp_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4455e1458819a9a93dcca4dac07cb"}}
