ApRqi-UpkwwLZKrRVdcrZlLpZGQs-xywv8zhWGxGMQrQHLHPNRhU1xCawSBRK2GD9vshyITrnWhm8DiF47kgdUZuuN3fDqsQvxO9f36ULd9gYTS2fhwnYAag-uSqSRx9YuIw5m3Pj1QX1xpxb6tBe-UQe1DO97vNGlLNaGNHGYQ9rmmwBdegm--y3xCV1HdiyfkY847dqNRm8possmeom2_dFbmX0lOsyYp-Qb-tOsHGB5AYnMdDsO8Z7LqWfxIKEWXRudvNpeqoEHFwZ2Ev6M1lz8Or1VxP_pFAWEkw4HS\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 学了。\n\n这条小红书的核心点我已经记住了：\n\n- **给 OpenClaw 安装 skill，不等于它在运行**\n- skill 很多时候只是：\n  - 一份说明\n  - 一套触发规则\n  - 一组可调用脚本/约定\n- **真正有没有在跑，要看执行链路**，不是看“装没装”\n\n以后我会按这个顺序判断：\n\n1. **有没有调度**\n   - OpenClaw cron jobs\n   - 系统 crontab\n   - heartbeat\n2. **有没有实际调用**\n   - 谁触发的\n   - 调了哪个脚本/哪个 job\n3. **有没有执行证据**\n   - run 记录\n   - session\n   - logs\n   - 输出文件\n4. **最后才谈这个 skill 有没有价值**\n\n换句话说：\n\n- **安装了 ≠ 运行中**\n- **定义了触发词 ≠ 一定会触发**\n- **有 SKILL.md ≠ 有后台守护进程**\n- **只有 run/session/log/产物 才算证据**\n\n这次我已经被你纠正过一轮了，后面我不会再把“看见装了 skill”当成“它一定在跑”的依据。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4460cc2e8819aac59e873687e9862\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":250651,"output":463,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":251114,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776567808748,"responseId":"resp_0b3ac7b405e714490169e4460304d0819aa18443ed1e88e720"}}
